        <p>
            <b>WHEREAS</b>
        </p>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>A.</b></td>
                <td>The immoveable properties situated at Hulikere Village, Belagola Hobli, Srirangapatna Taluk, Mandya District, Karnataka, were originally allotted to Mandya National Paper Mills Limited (“<b>MNPML</b>”) by the Government of Mysore as per the Mysore Gazette Notification dated April 14, 1961 bearing No. RDH 109 LCI 61 and possession was handed over to MNPML. Subsequently, MNPML was ordered to be wound up vide the order of the Hon’ble High Court of Karnataka in Company Petition bearing No. 112/1994 dated October 20, 2000, and the properties of MNPML were ordered to be put up for public auction, under the supervision of the Official Liquidator.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>B.</b></td>
                <td>The Promoter, earlier known as Anil Kumar M.N. Promoters Private Limited, purchased from the official liquidator appointed by the High Court of Karnataka in respect of the winding-up proceedings of MNPML, the immoveable properties bearing survey nos. 51/, 5/2, 5/3, 5/5, 7, 8/1, 8/2, 9/1, 9/2, 9/3, 10/1/, 10/2, 10/3, 11, 12, 104/1, 104/2, 105, 106/1, 106/2, 107/1, 107/2, 107/3, 107/4, 111/1A, 111/1B, 111/2, 121, 123,124, 147, 150 and 151 all forming a contiguous block having access to the main road, admeasuring 73 acres and  26  Guntas (Seventy Three Acres Twenty Six Guntas) situated at Hulikere Village, Belagola Hobli, Srirangapatna Taluk, Mandya District, Karnataka, (hereinafter referred to as the "<b>Said Land</b>") vide a sale deed dated December 12, 2007, registered as document bearing No. SRP-1-04879-2007-2008, stored in CD No. SRPD34. The said sale deed was rectified on September 26, 2008 by way of a registered document bearing No. SRP-1-02121-2008-2009, stored in CD No. SRPD40, in the office of the Sub-Registrar, Srirangapatna Taluk, Mandya District. Subsequently another rectification deed dated 14.10.2014 bearing Document No. SRP-1-03554-2014-15, stored in CD No. SRPD99, in the office of the Sub-Registrar, Srirangapatna Taluk, Mandya District was executed by the Official liquidator appointed by the High Court of Karnataka in favour of the promoter herein.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>C.</b></td>
                <td> The Promoter has conceived a scheme of development to develop the immoveable properties bearing survey nos. 5/1, 5/2, 5/3, 5/4, 5/5, 7, 8/1, 8/2,  9/1, 9/2, 9/3, 10/1, 10/2, 10/3, 11, 12, 104/1, 104/2, 105, 106/1, 106/2, 107/1, 107/2, 107/3, 107/4, 111/1A, 111/1B, 111/2, 121, 123, 124, 147, 150 and 151, admeasuring 73 Acres 26 Guntas situated at Hulikere Village, Belagola Hobli, Srirangapatna Taluk, Mandya District, Karnataka, into various phases which are developed at different point of time at the sole discretion and as per the policy decision of the Promoter. The said development is a mixed use development and the total development for the sake of identification only shall be known as Zuari Garden City. The Allottee is aware of the said scheme of Development of the Promoter and acknowledges that the said scheme of development is phase wise.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>D.</b></td>
                <td>The Promoter is developing the said Land into a residential township known as ‘<b>{!booking__c.Project1__r.Name}</b>’ 
                    (“Township”) and a portion of the said land measuring 10.04 Acres forming part of land under 
                    survey nos. 5/1, 105, 107/1, 107/2, 107/3, 107/4, 111/2, 111/1A, 111/1B, 121 &amp; 123 etc.,, herein after referred to as Project Land,
                    is being used for the purpose of developing plots in the name and style of Zuari Garden City-Plots (hereafter referred to as the “Project”)
                    and the Project Land is more fully described in the<b> Schedule A </b>hereunder (“<b>Schedule A Property</b>”).</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>E.</b></td>
                <td>The sanctioned plan and commencement certificate vide No. 208/2022-23, dated 21st March 2023 has been granted to the Promoter by Mysuru Urban 
                    Development Authority (MUDA). The Promoter agrees and undertakes that it shall not make any changes to these approved plans except in strict 
                    compliance with Section 14 of the Act and other laws as applicable and subject to approval of such modifications from MUDA.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>F.</b></td>
                <td>The Promoter has registered the Project under the provisions of the Act with the Karnataka Real Estate Regulatory Authority at Bangalore 
                    on 10.10.2023 vide Registration No.<b> PRM/KA/RERA/1267/374/PR/101023/006309</b> and the registration is valid and subsisting.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>G.</b></td>
                <td>The Allottee having gone through the relevant documents, being satisfied of the right, title and interest, having understood the entire scheme
