        </p>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>i</b></td>
                <td>The Total Price above includes the application money paid by the allottee to the Promoter towards application for purchase of the Plot</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>ii</b></td>
