            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b></b></td>
                <td>Provided that in case there is any change / modification in the taxes, the subsequent amount payable by the allottee to the promoter shall be increased/reduced based on such change / modification: </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b></b></td>
                <td>Provided further that if any increase in the taxes after the expiry of the schedule date of completion of the project as per registration with the authority which shall include the extension of registration, if any, granted to the said project by the Authority as per the Act, the same shall not be charged from the allottee</td>
