                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>1.4</b></td>
                <td>The Allottee(s) shall make the payment as per the payment plan set out in Schedule D (“Payment Plan”)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top" class="row1"><b>1.5</b></td>
